{"tid":1694159,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【市民拍照 警謊人員槍貼額頭恐嚇】","createTime":"2019-11-05T03:57:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-05T04:01:28.000Z","uid":162969,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"a062651e2d1d485c19706ab557102f5b9629ef8e","tid":1694159,"uid":162969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T03:57:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gTp9YGP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgTp9YGP.jpg&h=a8240831&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dOKU9Ou.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdOKU9Ou.jpg&h=6357683c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n四個多月來，警謊人員失控濫暴的情況，於鏡頭下無所遁形，而且情況愈來愈嚴重。<br />\n<br />\n11月2日晚11點32分，在砵蘭街肯德基快餐店對出位置，有警謊速龍正在拘捕一名受傷的市民，另一名市民見到，欲上前影相，但被一名速龍舉槍指嚇，槍口貼近額頭位置(可見照片上方黑色槍口)，相距不過數CM，極為恐怖驚人。<br />\n<br />\n該名市民並沒害怕，因其只想維護受傷被捕者的基本人權，故對警察說：「你物開槍囉！」<br />\n<br />\n該名警謊人員聽到後，退開，沒有開槍。<br />\n<br />\n攝影：香港市民<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/1432983410299343/posts/2425504397713901?d=n&amp;sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F1432983410299343%2Fposts%2F2425504397713901%3Fd%3Dn%26sfns%3Dmo&d=kDaEa4B9Gv5qH72Sa3%2FdwOCCrfoqRshWq79J%2FX5JLMA%3D&h=7e76d9b9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/1432983410299343/posts/2425504397713901?d=n&amp;sfns=mo</a>"},{"pid":"33711eb7a7b76c5874d6d2ad9cb39a3c7a009382","tid":1694159,"uid":268894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T04:01:28.000Z","msg":"嘩......好想打人呀!"}]}